answers.answer: What's the signs of that hun.  X
I'm so sorry  will be praying  for you and baby...I had preeclampsia With My First  Pregnancy and  Had  Emergency  C Section  At  32  Weeks

I was induced at 36 weeks with my oldest. It was a shock at first because I had to give up my idea of how I pictured things going. Once the induction started and it sank in a little more I was more excited. I was able to deliver vaginally which was what I wanted, thankfully they caught my pre
...eclampsia early... (Accidentally hit the post button mid sentence)

I had no signs of it. Until i went to the hospital for my contractions and when they checked my blood pressure it was high. Its never been high so they did blood work and another urine test and it came back... so they sent me home last night and i go back tomorrow morning to be induced.  Im hoping everything goes ok im so nervous
Just stay calm and try not to over analyze the situation, it will all work out. Keep your eyes on the prize!

I had it with my first and was induced at 37.5 weeks. :) she was a healthy 6lbs 1 1/4 oz. :) I'm currently 28 weeks with my second and already have high blood pressure and am on meds for it. I had her in 4 hours of induction! :) hoping the second goes as fast. As long as she is healthy I don't mind being induced again. I had her natural!

Had it with my second. Went in for my checkup at 39+2 weeks. Protein in urine, blood pressure a bit high..Dr had me go to labor and delivery that evening for cervadil induction. 12 hrs later, failure to progress (only a fingertip dilated), couldn't break water so was prepped for cesarean delivery. Way easier, however, had to recover 30min after surgery before I could hold my little man.

Well im already 3 cm dialated so im hoping when they induce it goes by quick . I want to go naturally no epidural. I hope the pain isnt as bad as i think .thank you ladies for your stories. I wish you all the best and healthy pregnancies.
Awww good luck . You'll have ur little one in your arms soon :-)

I had with my first, had been showing protein in urine for a few weeks but it wasnt caught until my last week of pregnancy and i was induced. They did the cervadil i think, it was 8 yrs ago, i started having contractions and my water broke the next morning and i was put on pitocin. I delivered vaginally.
